' Generated from source audit of agent/ - verified against report/agent/*.md
' Stereotypes:
'   <<singleton>>  : __new__-based singleton class
'   <<module>>     : Python module exposing only module-level functions (no class)
'   <<dataclass>>  : @dataclass
'   <<enum>>       : enum.Enum subclass
'   <<static>>     : class with only @staticmethod members
' Composition (*--) follows __init__() instantiation; aggregation (o--) follows
' setter/late-binding injection; dependency (..>) follows method-level usage.

